<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>New Device Login Detected - Dental Kit Store</title>
  </head>
  <body role="main">
    <h1>New Device Login Detected</h1>
    <p>Hello {{email}},</p>
    <p>A login to your account was detected from a new device or location:</p>
    <ul aria-label="Login details">
      <li><strong>Device:</strong> {{userAgent}}</li>
      <li><strong>IP Address:</strong> {{ip}}</li>
      <li><strong>Date/Time:</strong> {{date}}</li>
    </ul>
    <p>If this was you, you can safely ignore this email. If not, please reset your password immediately.</p>
    <hr>
    <p>&copy; {{year}} Dental Kit Store</p>
  </body>
</html> 